    <item>
      <title>印度股市现在比以往任何时候都更需要国内投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/india-s-stock-market-needs-domestic-investors-now-more-than-ever</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于外国基金抛售的持续进行和全球波动性的加剧削弱了本土股票的吸引力，印度股市对国内投资者的依赖从未如此强烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/india-s-stock-market-needs-domestic-investors-now-more-than-ever</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 07:37:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
